5eac70c2b1407","tid":1116001,"uid":235174,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:31:47.000Z","msg":"同當年屠猶一樣，因為本身響歐洲就不受歡迎，全世界扮睇唔到，重有勁多人和應<br />\n今日蛔一樣，本身唔受歡迎，助攻中共"},{"pid":"d4fc8d74b2e0bba54af0be80613f24df50c0d75e","tid":1116001,"uid":118976,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:32:15.000Z","msg":"如果捉唔到，係咪全組被罰<br />\n<br />\n什伍連坐法是西元前356年於秦國商鞅變法中的一種戶籍制度，將全國每五戶編成一伍，十戶編成一什，讓居民互相監督告密，如有「什」「伍」之中一戶犯罪，而其他戶不告密者，連坐腰斬。告密者得到的賞賜與在戰場上斬獲敵人首級等同，而知情不報者受到的懲罰，等同於「投降敵人」一樣的處罰。"},{"pid":"afd6e955c2266ca42f81944df461724fa8f8a4bd","tid":1116001,"uid":21378,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T18:38:25.000Z","msg":"地鐵安檢都係為咗防新疆人而設。"},{"pid":"c337defa3b8ccd2db4774916e336aae39d9584d1","tid":1116001,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T20:19:21.000Z","msg":"十字聯防我過波台睇唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a3b3e49ba81d64d3a2b8a1556e07d7499b64773","tid":1116001,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T23:11:53.000Z","msg":"根本即係新疆北韓化"},{"pid":"360996d07d509ce8b244065215c26ad580f19f4b","tid":1116001,"uid":233371,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T23:16:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ee194b56bcddb3cf02dcabf7999f63152044394","tid":1116001,"uid":233371,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T23:16:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54a4067554e8d5dc6244a6ded84bf38a68a8876d","tid":1116001,"uid":133319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T23:33:14.000Z","msg":"黐撚綫"},{"pid":"ee32c4a507901eb39268c8608e185e421d5724ee","tid":1116001,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"360996d07d509ce8b244065215c26ad580f19f4b","tid":1116001,"uid":233371,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T23:16:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T23:48:57.000Z